{"tid":2342850,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"濕疹好轉睇醫生問題","createTime":"2020-12-27T12:33:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T15:00:48.000Z","uid":298442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bf7131465f97691c5ff1cd62d2d90f995ab16dce","tid":2342850,"uid":298442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:33:32.000Z","msg":"如題，本身自己有濕疹都兩三年，其間不斷睇醫生搽類固醇越發越大，兩個月前的起心肝戒搽類固醇，正係搽Body lotion同戒口（唔食牛羊凍飲），點知最近濕疹有好轉唔再出水同埋開始唔痕同埋口，但係我Book左個皮膚科名醫？（要兩個月前Booking+第1次睇）<br />\n<br />\n想問下我應唔應該去睇醫生好呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原因係唔想洗咁多錢同埋驚佢再開類固醇藥比我"},{"pid":"eed0338c6bc5821dbbdab96217047f56abcc1fb0","tid":2342850,"uid":194281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:35:29.000Z","msg":"無咩事就咪鬼睇啦,西醫9成開類固醇"},{"pid":"4c2a0ca8888f0143da1fb61bee6429dd96dba2eb","tid":2342850,"uid":63177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:37:02.000Z","msg":"唔睇<br />\n你都有好轉啦<br />\n無謂以身試藥"},{"pid":"ecbdf9412c761fd45fb1cd3232ab630e61726a7b","tid":2342850,"uid":81973,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:38:56.000Z","msg":"唔好睇啊！要睇真係睇中醫！<br />\n睇西醫又係比類固醇<br />\n你會又重頭loop 真係唔好睇西醫"},{"pid":"7ea0fdc48ddb46bd40ff8595d64dd54835e609ca","tid":2342850,"uid":185224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:39:56.000Z","msg":"你呢個情況唔使睇<br />\n如果皮膚乾做好保濕 會好快啲同少啲痕<br />\n做下運動自然就會好 記撚住唔好再用類固醇"},{"pid":"0ec23dd6971ef45a88a960840f2f8cf61e7a552f","tid":2342850,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:40:14.000Z","msg":"記得保濕 aq cream<br />\n<br />\n醫生唔開類固醇都係開呢類軟膏<br />\n<br />\n另外可以試下食物敏感測試"},{"pid":"d63af0168670ab3883ce69316b6a881b12dff0cf","tid":2342850,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ec23dd6971ef45a88a960840f2f8cf61e7a552f","tid":2342850,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"